=Afarta Khulafo Raashidiinta=

[[Khaliif|Khulafo al-Rashiidiintu]] waa [[afar|afarta asxaabi]] ee hogaanka iyo talada maamulka dowlada [[Islaam]]ka la waday [[Nebi Muxamed]] intii uu noolaa isla markaana gacanta ku dhigay ayagoo iskaga dambeeyay hogaaminta dowladii Islaamka. Wakhtigii Khulafo al Raashidiinta dowlada Islaamku aad ayay u balaadhatay waxayna gaadhay meelo badan oo ka mid ah [[Bariga Dhexe]], [[Yurub|galbeedka qaarada Yurub]], [[Afrika|waqooyiga Afrika]], [[Aasiya|bariga fog]] iyo wadano aad u badan oo kale. 
Wakhtigani maamulka dowlada Islaamka ee [[Afarta Khulafo]] wuxuu bilaabmey [[bil|8dii Juune]] [[sanad|sanadkii 632 C.D]]; wuxuuna dhamaadaa [[wakhti|28 Luuliyo]] [[sanad|sanadkii 661 C.D]] taasi oo ku beegan goortii la dilay [[Cali|Cali binu Abi Dalib]] ee xilka iyo hogaanka dowlada Islaamka uu la wareegay [[Mucaawiya|Mucaawiya binu Abi Sufyaan]]. 
Intii [[Afarta Khulafo]] talada dowlada Islaamka hayeen waxay qabsadeen dhu aad u baaxad weynt taasi oo lagu qiyaaso [[km|9,000,000 km²]] ([[9|sagaal milyan mitir laba-laaban]])
(3,474,919 sq mi). 
Tirada dadka ku hoos jirey maamulka iyo hogaanka [[Khaliif|Khulafo al-Raashidiinta]] waxaa lagu sheegaa [[milyan|40,300,000]] (qiyaas dhan [[40|40 milyan]] oo qof).

